{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That metallic clank was so unbelievably penetrating that every time I hear something metallic fall on, say, cement or something and it makes that sound, I still jump.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because those doors, when they closed, it just meant, you know, the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the cattle car, no, we were hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was a very warm day in May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were so many people pushed so close together, we were hot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One woman gave birth in the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was not even room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was-- you know, not enough room for her to even lie down to give birth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Us kids tried to, like, you know, say that it won't be so bad and, you know, that the parents are thinking it's going to be much worse than it will be.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once we get out of the cattle cars, you know, we'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's just so suffocating in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have no air.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were saying, you know, that it's going to be OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But no, I don't remember any sense of humor in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think even the kids my age and a little older who were trying to make light of it were scared stiff, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was there a lot of weeping and crying?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the older people, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they frankly had no strength to cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the cattle car two days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, we arrived on the second day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they kept us in the cattle car for quite a while after we arrived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of the kids that were looking outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said that there were big smokestacks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we thought, well, that's the factories, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
